00:03:13.620 --> 00:03:18.120
facilities who had painted Mickey Mouse,&nbsp;
Minnie Mouse, and Goofy on their walls.

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:22.860
Which may sound severe, but we need to be&nbsp;
realistic with ourselves for a moment and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:22.860 --> 00:03:27.000
look at these cases for what they are,&nbsp;
which is intellectual property theft.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:30.240
If you head over to Disney's legal&nbsp;
department, their website states&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:35.220
that "You cannot legally make and sell&nbsp;
